ras/32298b993da87df826abded1660bb1b1.webp?t=1726842081\" width=615 height=54 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896950/extras/c4f85167818babf46d7ba3baeb31b2ee.poster.avif?t=1726842081\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896950/extras/c4f85167818babf46d7ba3baeb31b2ee.webm?t=1726842081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896950/extras/c4f85167818babf46d7ba3baeb31b2ee.mp4?t=1726842081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play as movie heroes Dr. Bravestone, Ruby, Mouse, and Prof. Shelly in a hilarious new 3D action adventure<br></li><li>In online or split-screen modes, work together with up to three friends or AI teammates to defeat enemies, survive deadly traps, and save the world <br></li><li>The world of Jumanji gets bigger with beautiful but deadly new mountain, city and jungle environments<br></li><li>As you hone your skills and strategies, and unlock new outfits and weapon styles, no two rounds of Jumanji are ever the same!</li></ul>",
